{C.PINK}
⠀⠀⠀⠀⣿⡇⠀⢸⣿⡇⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠸⠿⣿⣿⣿⡿⠿⠿⣿⣿⣿⣶⣄⠀
⠀⠀⢸⣿⣿⡇⠀⠀⠀⠈⣿⣿⣿⠀
⠀⠀⢸⣿⣿⡇⠀⠀⢀⣠⣿⣿⠟⠀
⠀⠀⢸⣿⣿⡿⠿⠿⠿⣿⣿⣥⣄⠀
⠀⠀⢸⣿⣿⡇⠀⠀⠀⠀⢻⣿⣿⣧
⠀⠀⢸⣿⣿⡇⠀⠀⠀⠀⣼⣿⣿⣿
⢰⣶⣿⣿⣿⣷⣶⣶⣾⣿⣿⠿⠛⠁
⠀⠀⠀⠀⣿⡇⠀⢸⣿⡇⠀⠀⠀⠀
{C.RST}
   {C.GRAY}v{VERSION} deepchaintk - Blockchain Forensics & Crypto OSINT{C.RST}
   {C.GRAY}Developed by Nixovena Labs{C.RST}
